flowchart LR
    A1.1[Read / Tile A/01] --> A1.2[Resample]
    A2.1[Read / Tile A/02] --> A2.2[Resample]
    A1.2 --> A1.3[NDVI]
    A2.2 --> A2.3[NDVI]
    A1.3 & A2.3 --> CO1[Collocation]
    CO1 --> BM1[Band Math / Max value]

    B1.1[Read / Tile B/01] --> B1.2[Resample]
    B2.1[Read / Tile B/02] --> B2.2[Resample]
    B1.2 --> B1.3[NDVI]
    B2.2 --> B2.3[NDVI]
    B1.3 & B2.3 --> CO2[Collocation]
    CO2 --> BM2[Band Math / Max value]

    BM1 & BM2 --> M[Mosaic]

    M --> W[Write]